| 2 | {Decision point}        | {Chosen approach}   | {Alt 1}, {Alt 2}             | {Why chosen over alternatives}         |
| 3 | {Decision point}        | {Chosen approach}   | {Alt 1}, {Alt 2}             | {Why chosen over alternatives}         |

